ow-hidden flex flex-col pb-16 md:pb-0"},["DIV",{"class":"flex flex-col h-full max-w-2xl mx-auto w-full p-6"},["DIV",{"class":"flex items-center justify-between mb-12"},["DIV",{},["H2",{"class":"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-text-main"},"主动召回"],["P",{"class":"text-sm text-text-muted"},"今天需要强化 ","5"," 个概念。"]],["DIV",{"class":"px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-secondary border border-border-main text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-text-sub shadow-sm"},"1"," / ","5"]],["DIV",{"class":"flex-1 flex flex-col items-center justify-center perspective-1000 relative p-4"},["DIV",{"class":"absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center -z-10 pointer-events-none opacity-20 md:opacity-40"},["DIV",{"class":"w-[300px] h-[300px] opacity-40 pointer-events-none"},["svg",{"width":"300","height":"300"}]]],["DIV",{"class":"relative w-full max-w-md aspect-[3/4] md:aspect-[4/3] cursor-pointer preserve-3d","style":"transform: none;"},["DIV",{"class":"absolute inset-0 bg-card border border-border-main rounded-[24px] md:rounded-[32px] p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center backface-hidden shadow-2xl"},["DIV",{"class":"absolute top-6 left-6 md:top-8 md:left-8 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-black text-accent opacity-50"},"问题"],["DIV",{"class":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium leading-relaxed text-text-main MarkdownCardWrapper"},["P",{},"小明写了一个递归函数计算斐波那契数列 fib(n)，当 n=50 时程序卡住了很久才出结果。请从调用栈和时间复杂度的角度解释原因，并说明解决方案。"]],["DIV",{"class":"absolute bottom-6 md:bottom-8 text-[10px] md:text-xs text-text-muted font-bold uppercase tracking-widest animate-pulse"},"点击显示答案"]],["DIV",{"class":"absolute inset-0 bg-card border border-accent/30 rounded-[24px] md:rounded-[32px] p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center backface-hidden shadow-2xl [transform:rotateY(180deg)]"},["DIV",{"class":"absolute top-6 left-6 md:top-8 md:left-8 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-black text-green-500/50"},"答案"],["DIV",{"class":"text-lg md:text-xl text-text-sub leading-relaxed MarkdownCardWrapper"},["P",{},"原因在于指数级时间复杂度：fib(50)需要计算fib(49)和fib(48)，而fib(49)又要计算fib(48)和fib(47)，导致fib(48)、fib(47)等大量子问题被重复计算，总调用次数约等于斐波那契数本身（≈O(2ⁿ)）。"],"\n",["P",{},"底层逻辑：递归树中存在大量重叠子问题，每次函数调用都会创建新的栈帧，50层深的调用链意味着数千次函数调用和栈帧操作。"],"\n",["P",{},"解决方案：记忆化（Memoization）——用字典缓存已计算的结果，使每个子问题只计算一次，时间复杂度降为O(n)。"]]]]]]]]],[[15,289]],[[15,290]]]],"viewport":{"width":1200,"height":745},"timestamp":216268.574,"wallTime":1774816278968,"collectionTime":0.6000000014901161,"resourceOverrides":[],"isMainFrame":true}}
